item.title: KeyError Problems
item.description: During my schooling, cleaning was really only covered regarding spreadsheets. Even in the advanced courses, where python dominates, there is little coverage on what using pre-compiled datasets and handling any problems you come across. So, as I run into them, I will be logging them here and other posts as required depending on the error type.
